@wowcabbage
turn your router off?. You could just open Network and sharing centre-> change adapter settings -> right-click on Local Area Network -> disable it. Then re-enable it again when done. A faster way is to use the quicklaunch icon (small monitor icon beside the clock).
Or like me, use kaspersky firewall to block Tropico4.exe. Windows firewall just doesn't work, and btw alot more confusing @@.
